data.description: Peace and Tranquility on the PRESERVE ..At APEX PARK CENTRAL Embark into your very own Sanctuary! This 3/2 corner unit is on the FIRST FLOOR, One story unit with its very own little yard/Covered patio for entertaining. Alexa/Smart Home with Open concept, updated kitchen and stackable washer and dryer. Kitchen has a huge quartz island with stainless steal appliances, Impact resistant windows and doors. This perfect little home is ready for a new family to enjoy! This is RESORT Style living at its finest with a Beautiful Clubhouse / zero entry pool and multiple play areas for children. Also, enjoy jogging paths, restaurants, entertainment and A+ Schools. Enjoy Luxurious amenities such as state of the art fitness center, BBQ areas, tennis/pickle ball, sauna, basketball and MORE!
